item.description:
The 2nd Annual Celtic 5K will take place on Sunday, March 11, 2012 in Worcester, MA. The race will start at 11:00 a.m. at Elm Park and will be an out and back loop on the annual Worcester Saint Patrick's Day Parade route. Thousands of people will be cheering on runners and walkers as they celebrate Saint Patrick. The Celtic 5K will be the third and final race in the "Tour de Patrick" race series.

For more information go to www.celtic5k.com
